io.smudgr.engine

Class SmudgeComponentLibrary<T extends SmudgeComponent>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.smudgr.app.project.reflect.ReflectionLibrary<T>
      • io.smudgr.engine.SmudgeComponentLibrary<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The ReflectableType this Library should manage

    public class SmudgeComponentLibrary<T extends SmudgeComponent>
extends ReflectionLibrary<T>
    A SmudgeComponentLibrary provides the ability to detect and organize all loaded concrete implementations of a given ReflectableType
